# Keep the build context small. The server image (server/Dockerfile) only COPYs shared/ +
# server/, and the web image (deploy/web/Dockerfile) builds the client — so the context must
# include the client source, public assets, and scripts, but never node_modules / build output.
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/*.tsbuildinfo
.git
.github
.claude
docs
*.log
.DS_Store
